kinds of massive YouTubers doing

00:22:44.871 --> 00:22:46.971
philanthropic work in their videos?

00:22:47.363 --> 00:22:49.621
Praiseworthy and good, deceptive and

00:22:49.631 --> 00:22:51.831
dangerous, or somewhere in between?

